## üìÅ Project Structure

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ archi/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ broker.py       # Orchestrates emitter/consumer coordination
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ emitter.py      # Emits to broker
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ consumer.py     # Handles post-resolution logic
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ events.py       # Internal event bus
tests/
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ test_*.py       # Full pytest-asyncio test suite
main.py                 # Example use case
pyproject.toml          # Build + metadata
```

